At 14pm on February 2, Xiaoyang boarded a flight to Wuhan as a medical staff member of a volunteer medical support team. This is him talking to his boyfriend, Raymond, right before he turned it off.

In the early morning of Sunday, February 2, Xiaoyang received the Wechat of the hospital's leadership, ready to personal items, stand by. We're finally going to the hot zone.

Although he handed in the invitation to the war when he was ready, however, in the received notice of that moment, or Xiaoyang some panic. He was one of the most junior members of the second medical team. Faced with the huge epidemic and the rising number of infections and deaths every day, he said, "I'm not afraid. That's not true. " But Xiaoyang has supported outbreaks of influenza a and bird flu, and went to Wenchuan County for medical aid after the earthquake. He knew: "put on the white clothes, saving lives is my bounden duty. "

At the airport, friends with supplies to Xiaoyang they see off, said not to cry, the result of friends or holding Xiaoyang cry into tears. Xiaoyang said to her: "Well, I will come back in one piece, safe and sound, don't worry. "

"Beijing, Beijing, I'm leaving. I sincerely hope that when I return, we can take off our masks and see each other's smiles! " The 135 people on the plane were all doctors and nurses supporting Wuhan, they will be in the worst places for the fighting to come.

At 16:34, Xiaoyang and his colleagues arrived at Wuhan Tianhe Airport.

On his second day in Wuhan, Xiao Yang learned from fellow doctors that the situation was still critical and that many patients were waiting for hospital beds.

Although he was told that the hospital was recruiting medical and nursing personnel to go to the front line, Xiaoyang immediately signed up, but this epidemic was so serious that he was also very upset, "The COVID-19 can be transmitted by inhalation, by droplets, by faecal-oral transmission, the virus can mutate rapidly, and it is not known if there are any new routes of transmission. " But seeing the severity of the outbreak in Wuhan, Xiaoyang felt it might have to wait until it was under control.

Now, medical supplies in the epidemic area are tight. In order to carry out this campaign, the hospital in Xiaoyang supported the hospital in Wuhan with protective clothing. Therefore, everyone did not bring protective clothing. They said there would be one in the hospital in Wuhan, but today we learned that the hospital they supported, there's very little protection. And I don't have any groceries. I have to make my own. Boyfriend arrives at the scene with a bunch of stuff he doesn't need. Tonight will be put to work, there will be patients in the evening, so Xiaoyang while the afternoon will be free, to the supermarket to life necessities.

In addition to Washbasin toothbrushes, Xiao Yang also bought a lot of Adult diaper. Because of the serious shortage of protective clothing, each protective clothing should be worn as long as possible, and the work time should be at least five to six hours. If you go to the toilet, you should take off the protective clothing, it takes a long time to undress, and you have to shower before you put on your new suit for at least half an hour, so in order to save time and not to wear the suit too much, the staff will work in a diaper, and the urine will be taken out in the diaper inside the suit.

Dozens of beds have been opened up in the hospital where Xiaoyang is based to receive critically ill patients with new pneumonia. The Sun will go to war tonight.

Boyfriend in fact do not want Xiaoyang to come, very worried, but still "know roughly" to choose to support the work of Xiaoyang. Neither Xiaoyang nor Raymond had a good Spring Festival. Xiaoyang spent the holiday in the hospital, while Raymond, who works as a police officer, was also on the front line of the epidemic. During this time, he often had to work outdoors, going to the railway station, where there was a heavy flow of people, to ensure the safety of the people.

Raymond says he understands Xiaoyang's work and is used to it. "where? What's the patient's condition? Well, I'll go right away! ! " Xiaoyang hung up the phone and began to dress, often in the early morning sleepy eyes, was awakened by the sudden call. Xiaoyang light hand light feet get up, put on the suit smartly, simple tidying up a while, quietly took the door to go.

Instead of pretending not to be woken, Raymond reached out to feel the warm half of the bed, unable to sleep for a long time. Only a silent prayer: "in the life and death of the rescue line, I would like you to have the best state, to deal with the worst of all situations. Dear Bao, the patient is healthy and safe! You come back early. "

Xiao Yang is a male nurse in the emergency room of the hospital. Every day, he encounters patients who are either critical or urgent. Male nurses are "strong and strong" in the department. They always have to do more. Xiaoyang is always wearing a green dress, a pair of white shoes, with a cartoon pattern with a nurse's hat, capable and agile, do not neglect, do not hesitate to protect the health of patients. As a gay man, he was more empathetic and considerate, and the care in his eyes often brought warmth to the patients in the ward.

With a health care worker at home, Raymond had become accustomed to making late night visits. Once, on a chilly winter evening, Raymond took Xiaoyang by the hand and sent him to work. A block ahead of the hospital, suddenly in front of a noisy, the original person fainted. Xiao Yang stepped up, crowded the crowd, squat down, kneeling in the ice and snow mixed road, check the situation of the fallen. The person who fell to the ground did not have consciousness, did not breath, did not have the heartbeat, Xiao Yang turns round to shout to Raymond "quick to make 120! " , immediately after bends down the body, starts to press. Still do not forget to call back: "There is no family? " 1,2,3,4, very hard, the weather is very cold, breath in between the nose and mouth filled, Xiaoyang has been kneeling in the snow. An ambulance arrived, and as they sped off, Raymond headed home to Florida to find dry clothes to change her wet knees.

I had a nurse at home who was more of an apology than an understanding, because Raymond was a cop who worked the same One Call Away hours. At any time the sudden police situation, let him leave the same hard Xiaoyang many times, rushed away from home police.

Small two people in the world, there are always such an emergency, a house call, a call, the only time together, often encounter interruptions. How to balance, how to choose, how to take into account? The two of them chose to support each other.

They know: Life is bound, life is entrusted to them. One to keep the people healthy, the other to keep one side safe.

Raymond often picked up Xiaoyang from work and scoured the busy crowd for the little flower hat. See doctors and nurses dressed in a symbol of the green busy life, they shuttle between patients in need of care, like angels.

Parents Know Xiaoyang and boyfriend of many years of feelings, but the attitude has not been very supportive. I asked Xiaoyang if he wanted to post the article on the public account. He said he wanted to post it on the friends and Relatives Association account so that Gay parents could see that gay children are also very responsible and responsible.

Let's hope the outbreak is over soon. Tonight, Xiao Yang will wear protective clothing to start busy for patients. I wish Xiaoyang an early safe return, I hope all the angels in white are healthy and safe!
